Sternotherus odoratus (Eastern Musk Turtle) Distribution

Lyranda Thiem

library(dismo)
extent <- extent(-130,-70,20,40)

pilo_dismo <- gbif("sternotherus", species = "odoratus", ext = extent,
             geo = TRUE, sp = TRUE, download = TRUE,
             removeZeros = TRUE)
## Loading required namespace: jsonlite
## 4230 records found
## 0-300-600-900-1200-1500-1800-2100-2400-2700-3000-3300-3600-3900-4200-4230 records downloaded
library(ggplot2)
## 
## Attaching package: 'ggplot2'
## The following object is masked from 'package:latticeExtra':
## 
##     layer
## The following object is masked from 'package:ggridges':
## 
##     scale_discrete_manual
pilo_xy2 <- as.data.frame(cbind(pilo_dismo@coords[,1],pilo_dismo@coords[,2]))
colnames(pilo_xy2) <- c("longitude","latitude")

us <- map_data("state")


ggplot(data = pilo_xy2, aes(x=longitude, y=latitude)) +
  geom_polygon(data = us, aes(x=long, y = lat, group = group),
               fill = "white", color="black") +
  geom_point() + xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude")
